reviewText: LOVE, LOVE, LOVE THIS SERIES! Purchased the DVD, Participant's Guide and devotional! MUST HAVES! Perfect for a Bible study group. And not just for the ladies either, this is perfect for guys as well. Perfect condition. Quick shipping.

After doing the Made to Crave bible study our group decided to follow up with the Action plan and we are very glad we did.  the additional information we are getting from it is invaluable.  we would highly recommend it for anyone who has done the bible study.
I wasn't happy with it, was very basic and not very much helpful information.  Felt the presentations were a bit condescending.  Just my opinion!
